&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2025-03-21:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; Michael Ignatieff, who headed up CEU in Budapest, on &lt;a href=&quot;https://archive.ph/20250314193712/https://www.chronicle.com/article/how-a-university-fights-an-authoritarian-regime&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;what US edus should do&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;external-icon&quot; style=&quot;max-width:0.8em;max-height:0.8em&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2025-03-21:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; I was sure that &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wired.com/story/tesla-cybertrucks-made-with-the-wrong-glue-hit-with-yet-another-sticky-recall/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Tesla coined&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;external-icon&quot; style=&quot;max-width:0.8em;max-height:0.8em&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; the fabulous word “embrittlement,” &lt;a href=&quot;https://books.google.com/ngrams/graph?content=embrittlement&amp;#x26;year_start=1800&amp;#x26;year_end=2022&amp;#x26;corpus=en&amp;#x26;smoothing=3&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;but it was far more popular in 1967 and 1983&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;external-icon&quot; style=&quot;max-width:0.8em;max-height:0.8em&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
