&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;../img/2025-03-24-i-survived-college-without-becoming-a-liberal.jpg&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; height=&quot;auto&quot; alt=&quot;wmed relative|center&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
